title: Multiple compartment square food container

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a multiple compartment square food container, as shown and described.

FIG. 6 is a front elevational view thereof, shown enlarged for detail;
FIG. 7 is a rear elevational view thereof, shown enlarged for detail;
